 inspiring message for us all. The power is not in the hands of the elites, Catalonia shows that it is in the power of hard working, motivated, globally networked, hopeful people.","markups":[]},{"name":"d1a6","type":11,"text":"Catalans in 100 cities all over the world created their own human\nV for Vote demonstrations","markups":[],"layout":1,"iframe":{"mediaResourceId":"195fdd81f4d48b5298b07c6d84b9a48c","iframeWidth":854,"iframeHeight":480}},{"name":"6402","type":1,"text":"Let’s stand up for the Catalan right to vote.","markups":[]}],"sections":[{"name":"c27d","startIndex":0}]},"postDisplay":{"coverless":true}},"media":null,"virtuals":{"currentCollectionId":"","statusForCollection":"","createdAtRelative":"19 days ago","updatedAtRelative":"16 days ago","acceptedAtRelative":"","createdAtEnglish":"September 10, 2014","updatedAtEnglish":"September 13, 2014","acceptedAtEnglish":"","firstPublishedAtEnglish":"September 10, 2014","latestPublishedAtEnglish":"September 13, 2014","allowNotes":true,"languageTier":1,"snippet":"Catalans will come out en masse Thursday to demand the right to vote on independence on the 300th anniversary of the loss of their…","previewImage":{"imageId":"1*cMStvPS_PamDbHS0gD_ofA.jpeg","filter":"","backgroundSize":"contain","originalWidth":1024,"originalHeight":575,"strategy":"resample","height":0,"width":0},"wordCount":2294,"imageCount":5,"readingTime":9.489937106918239,"draftSnippet":"Catalans will come out en masse Thursday to demand the right to vote on independence on the 300th anniversary of the loss of their…","subtitle":"Catalans will come out en masse Thursday to demand the right to vote on independence on the 300th anniversary of the loss of their…","isOnReadingList":false,"postedIn":[],"publishedInCount":0,"usersBySocialRecommends":[],"notesBySocialRecommends":[],"proposedAtRelative":"","latestPublishedAtAbbreviated":"Sep 13","firstPublishedAtAbbreviated":"Sep 10","emailSnippet":"Catalans will come out en masse Thursday to demand the rig